import React from 'react'
import styled from 'styled-components'

const Container = styled.div`
height:60px;
`
const Left = styled.div`

`

function Navbar() {
    return (
        
        <Container>
            <Left>
                Left
            </Left>
            Navbar
           
        </Container>
    )
}

export default Navbar
